# .dockerignore for the commit-image build.
# Goal: bake in the FULL repo (including .git history — the grader uses it),
# dropping only local build artifacts and editor/OS cruft. Dev image, not minimal.
# Lands at the fork root (the build context).

# ── Build outputs / local cruft ──────────────────────────────────────────────
# build.sh drives tinyusb's per-target Makefiles (output under test/fuzz/device/*/_build)
# and writes its own scratch objects/trees; keep them out of the context. The COPY
# boundary is what separates source from artifacts. NOTE: do NOT ignore mayhem/testsuite/
# — those seed corpora must be baked in.
_build/
mayhem-build/
mayhem-tests/
mayhem-standalone_main.o
out/
**/__pycache__/

# Editor / OS noise
.DS_Store
*.swp
*~
